    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mosques having a vast rectangular hall, generally a flat roof, and whose interior is divided by many rows of columns.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
